Taken from [EmacsWiki](http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/autotest.el)
author: [Ryan Davis](http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/RyanDavis)

Sets up an autotest buffer and provides convenience methods.

---

This is a fork of krick's fork of Ryan Davis original autotest.el.

I needed the ansi color support of krick's version, but I wanted to backport Ryan's modifications, that's how this fork was born.